message: “A report from The U.S. Department of Health & Human Services estimates that between 240,000 & 325,000 children are at risk for sexual exploitation each year.”  Tonight, 6 pm EST  Jon Scott  provides an in-depth look at Human Trafficking on Fox Report Weekend .

attachments.media_description: Human trafficking victims recount tales of being forced into modern-day slavery: 'It was a living hell'
